message.body: Hey! When you get to the Hilton Harrisburg, there is an alley around back the hotel that has the entrance to the parking lot special for the hotel.
Make sure to get a ticket and that is charged to the room when you check in
I just checked in. Just seeing if y'all are up or already sleeping.
I was totally passed out. Meeting Bev in the lobby at 8:30 to head over to location. Meet us down there!
